sphinx-revealjs
===============

.. image:: https://github.com/attakei/sphinx-revealjs/workflows/Testings/badge.svg
    :target: https://github.com/attakei/sphinx-revealjs/actions

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/nine.svg
